{{mergeto|Racial formation theory|Talk:Racialization#Merger proposal|date=May 2008}}

'''Racialization''' refers to processes of the discursive production of [[Race (classification of human beings)|racial identities]]. It signifies the extension of racial meanings to a previously racially unclassified relationship, social practice, or group.<ref name=Omi & Winant 1986>Omi & Winant 1986.</ref>
